{"tid":251829,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾欣桐並無出席「貞潔校園開學禮」！","createTime":"2017-05-21T09:19:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T16:38:57.000Z","uid":97606,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36b4c96126349b8255a4b0ded23ca86a16db3b1a","tid":251829,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:19:39.000Z","msg":"明報歡迎網民轉載 但勿竄改新聞報道 2008年2月13日<br />\n　　<br />\n【明報專訊】明報發現，近日有網民在不同網上討論區內引述本報2006年9月3日的一篇報道，指藝人鍾欣桐曾於2006年9月2日出席由大衛城文化中心主辦的「貞潔校園開學禮」，<span style=\"color: red;\">並呼籲學生拒絕婚前性行為。</span><br />\n　　<br />\n經編輯部查證，網上討論區內的報道與明報當天的報道不符&mdash;&mdash;明報當天的報道，指出「近千名基督徒出席由大衛城文化中心主辦的貞潔校園開學禮，除譴責《壹本便利》偷拍鍾欣桐更衣之外，亦呼籲學生拒絕婚前性行為」，整篇報道都沒有提及鍾欣桐有份出席活動或作出呼籲，特此澄清以正視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n　　<br />\n明報歡迎網民轉載相關報道，但請勿竄改，以保持內容正確，多謝合作。"},{"pid":"bc214a57d2cbec02930181c2e2d0798e35eb8343","tid":251829,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:20:55.000Z","msg":"明報歡迎網民轉載相關報道，但請勿竄改，以保持內容正確，多謝合作。"},{"pid":"3d9a90d86b078b617cc88b4f6982d1916ead4366","tid":251829,"uid":97606,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>明報歡迎網民轉載相關報道，但請勿竄改，以保持內容正確，多謝合作。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"http://i18.photobucket.com/albums/b114/happy4ever76/hmmm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi18.photobucket.com%2Falbums%2Fb114%2Fhappy4ever76%2Fhmmm.jpg&h=021d8871&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9aabd75f393b12bde4d658bdcf73a9875a9d1920","tid":251829,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T09:23:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcR4CS8Sb0ByNJyACFlNepZwO4PdE-oTW8SjS_w8iNVBkqvWKgbP5w\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcR4CS8Sb0ByNJyACFlNepZwO4PdE-oTW8SjS_w8iNVBkqvWK